---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Spotlight from '../components/Spotlight.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact - Nidhi Mehta Interior Design" description="Start your interior design journey with transparent pricing. Virtual-first boutique design studio serving Vadodara.">
	<Navigation />

	<!-- Hero Section - Dark (Preserved) -->
	<section class="pt-32 pb-12 px-4 bg-black relative overflow-hidden">
		<Spotlight className="-top-40 left-0 md:left-60 md:-top-20" fill="#D8BFD8" />
		<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
			<h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-display-sm md:text-display leading-none tracking-tighter-xl mb-6 text-text">
				Let's Create Your <span class="bg-gradient-primary bg-clip-text text-transparent">Dream Space</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-text-light leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				We come to you — no office visits needed. Choose the package that fits your budget and how involved you want to be.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Pricing Section - Light Theme -->
	<section class="py-12 px-4 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-200">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
			<div class="text-center mb-10">
				<h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-3">
					Simple, Honest Pricing
				</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
					No hidden charges. No confusing quotes. What you see is what you pay.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Entry Point Package - Featured with Gradient -->
			<div class="mb-10">
				<div class="bg-gradient-primary text-black border-2 border-primary p-6 md:p-8 relative rounded-lg shadow-lg">
					<div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 px-4 py-1 bg-white border-2 border-primary text-black text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-full">
						Start Here
					</div>
					<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center">
						<div class="text-left">
							<h3 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Quick Discovery Call</h3>
							<div class="flex items-baseline mb-3">
								<span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">₹499</span>
								<span class="ml-2 opacity-80">for 15 minutes</span>
							</div>
							<p class="opacity-90 text-base">
								Not sure where to start? Let's have a quick chat to understand your needs and budget.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm md:text-base text-left">
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
									</svg>
									What you want for your home
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
									</svg>
									Budget that works for you
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
									</svg>
									Which package is right for you
								</li>
							</ul>
							<a href="#booking" class="inline-block mt-4 px-6 py-3 bg-black text-white font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-sm hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer rounded shadow-md">
								Book a Call
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Main Pricing Cards - 2x2 Grid - Light Theme -->
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
				<!-- Package 1: Consultation -->
				<div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-primary hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 p-6 rounded-lg">
					<div class="mb-4">
						<h3 class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Just the Design Ideas</h3>
						<div class="flex items-baseline mb-2">
							<span class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary">₹2,999</span>
							<span class="text-gray-600 ml-2 text-sm">one session</span>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs text-primary font-medium">
							Money back if you choose a bigger package later
						</p>
					</div>

					<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-sm">
						<strong class="text-black">Good for:</strong> People who want to do it themselves with our guidance
					</p>

					<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-6">
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							90-minute meeting at your home or video call
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							We'll understand your space and what you need
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							Design suggestions and color ideas
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							Material and furniture recommendations
						</li>
					</ul>

					<a href="#booking" class="block text-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-sm hover:bg-primary hover:text-black transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer rounded">
						Book Now
					</a>
				</div>

				<!-- Package 2: Design Drawings -->
				<div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-primary hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 p-6 rounded-lg">
					<div class="mb-4">
						<h3 class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Complete Design Plans</h3>
						<div class="flex items-baseline mb-2">
							<span class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary">₹15K+</span>
							<span class="text-gray-600 ml-2 text-sm">per room</span>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs text-gray-600">
							Final cost depends on room size
						</p>
					</div>

					<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-sm">
						<strong class="text-black">Good for:</strong> You'll handle contractors, we give you the full plan
					</p>

					<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-6">
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							Detailed drawings with exact measurements
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							3D pictures so you can see how it'll look
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							What materials to buy and where
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							All files you can share with your carpenter
						</li>
					</ul>

					<a href="#booking" class="block text-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-sm hover:bg-primary hover:text-black transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer rounded">
						Get Started
					</a>
				</div>

				<!-- Package 3: Design + Partnership (Most Popular) -->
				<div class="bg-gradient-primary text-black border-2 border-primary p-6 relative rounded-lg shadow-lg">
					<div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 px-3 py-1 bg-white border-2 border-primary text-black text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-full">
						Most People Choose This
					</div>
					<div class="mb-4 pt-2">
						<h3 class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Design + We Guide You</h3>
						<div class="flex items-baseline mb-2">
							<span class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">6-10%</span>
							<span class="ml-2 text-sm opacity-80">of total cost</span>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs opacity-80">
							You manage workers, we help you
						</p>
					</div>

					<p class="mb-4 text-sm opacity-90">
						<strong>Good for:</strong> You want to save money but need expert help
					</p>

					<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm mb-6">
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							Everything from design plans package
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							We'll connect you with good carpenters
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							Regular site visits to check the work
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							Help buying materials at best prices
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							You pay workers directly (save money!)
						</li>
					</ul>

					<a href="#booking" class="block text-center px-6 py-3 bg-black text-white font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-sm hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer rounded shadow-md">
						Popular Choice
					</a>
				</div>

				<!-- Package 4: Turnkey -->
				<div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-primary hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 p-6 rounded-lg">
					<div class="mb-4">
						<h3 class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Full Service - We Do Everything</h3>
						<div class="flex items-baseline mb-2">
							<span class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary">10-15%</span>
							<span class="text-gray-600 ml-2 text-sm">of total cost</span>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs text-gray-600">
							Sit back and relax
						</p>
					</div>

					<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-sm">
						<strong class="text-black">Good for:</strong> Busy people who don't have time to manage
					</p>

					<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-6">
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							We handle everything from start to finish
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							We find and manage all workers
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							Daily updates on progress
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							We buy all materials for you
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
							</svg>
							Guaranteed completion date
						</li>
					</ul>

					<a href="#booking" class="block text-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-sm hover:bg-primary hover:text-black transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer rounded">
						Easy Option
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Trust Elements -->
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-600">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
					<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
					</svg>
					<span>Written agreement for everything</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
					<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
					</svg>
					<span>No surprise charges later</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
					<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z" />
					</svg>
					<span>Answer all calls and messages</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- FAQ Section - Light Theme -->
	<section class="py-12 px-4 bg-white border-t border-gray-200">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<div class="text-center mb-10">
				<h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-3">
					Common Questions
				</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
					Everything you want to know before we start.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="space-y-4">
				<!-- FAQ 1 -->
				<details class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-5 cursor-pointer group rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition-colors">
					<summary class="font-heading text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-black list-none flex justify-between items-center">
						Do you visit for free to see my home?
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
						<p>
							We charge ₹2,999 for the first visit because we take it seriously. In that 90 minutes, we'll give you real design ideas, color suggestions, and a clear plan — not just a quick look around.
						</p>
						<p>
							The best part? If you choose any design package after, this ₹2,999 gets adjusted in your total cost. So it's basically free if you work with us.
						</p>
					</div>
				</details>

				<!-- FAQ 2 -->
				<details class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-5 cursor-pointer group rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition-colors">
					<summary class="font-heading text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-black list-none flex justify-between items-center">
						Why don't you have an office?
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						<p>
							We work from home and come to your place instead. This saves us rent, and we pass those savings to you with lower prices. Plus, we need to see your actual space to design it properly — not just show you pictures in an office.
						</p>
					</div>
				</details>

				<!-- FAQ 3 -->
				<details class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-5 cursor-pointer group rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition-colors">
					<summary class="font-heading text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-black list-none flex justify-between items-center">
						Can I upgrade my package later?
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						<p>
							Yes! Many people start with just design ideas or plans, then later ask us to help with the full work. We'll credit what you've already paid toward the bigger package.
						</p>
					</div>
				</details>

				<!-- FAQ 4 -->
				<details class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-5 cursor-pointer group rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition-colors">
					<summary class="font-heading text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-black list-none flex justify-between items-center">
						What does 6-10% mean exactly?
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
						<p>
							Let's say your total project will cost ₹2 lakhs (for materials, carpenter, electrician, etc.). With our 6-10% partnership package, our fee would be ₹12,000 to ₹20,000.
						</p>
						<p>
							For that, we give you the complete design, help you find good workers, guide you on buying materials, and regularly check the work quality. You handle the workers directly and pay them, which helps you save money.
						</p>
					</div>
				</details>

				<!-- FAQ 5 -->
				<details class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-5 cursor-pointer group rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition-colors">
					<summary class="font-heading text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-black list-none flex justify-between items-center">
						What's NOT included in your packages?
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						<p>
							Our fees are just for the design and our services. The actual cost of materials (wood, tiles, paint), furniture, carpenter's charges, electrician charges — those are separate. We'll tell you exactly how much all of that will cost before we start.
						</p>
					</div>
				</details>

				<!-- FAQ 6 -->
				<details class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-5 cursor-pointer group rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition-colors">
					<summary class="font-heading text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-black list-none flex justify-between items-center">
						Can I pay in installments?
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						<p>
							Yes. For bigger projects, we split the payment into parts — some at the start, some when design is ready, some during work, and final payment after everything is done. We'll discuss this when we meet.
						</p>
					</div>
